text:
Memoir kya likhe jab har pal anokhe anubhav sa beeta ho, kisi pal ko agar likho toh kisi aur pal ke saath na-insaafi hogi, isiliye sirf kuch panktiyan.
Na jaane kitni kahani aur kitne saare kisse, kuch khatte aur bahut se meethe, bas aisihi raha hai yeh safar. 
Har mod ne kuch naya sikhaya, bahut hasaya fir khub rulaya. 
Bahut shukriya is safar me mera saath nibhane ka, bahut kuch sunne ka aur kuch sunnane ka. 
Abhi toh kayi kahaniyan likni baaki hai, kayi kisse sunnen baki hai, yeh toh bas shuruat hai jaaneman, picture abhi kafi baaki hai.
